data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Excited to announce that this beautiful home was just appraised and is listed below the appraised value. Let me paint a picture for you of this newly & completely renovated single-family home. Nestled in the heart of Valrico, this stunning residence is the epitome of modern elegance and charm. Boasting a fresh and contemporary interior design, this home offers an ideal sanctuary for those seeking both comfort and style.As you step onto the beautiful front porch then through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting and open floor plan that seamlessly blends functionality with a touch of luxury. The spacious living area features ample natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere that is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The gourmet kitchen is an absolute dream come true for any aspiring chef. With stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, and sleek countertops, this space is as functional as it is visually appealing. Whether you're hosting family gatherings or enjoying a quiet meal at home, this kitchen will exceed your every expectation.The home offers a generous master suite that is a true retreat from the outside world. Complete with a walk-in closet and a spa-like ensuite bathroom, a rain head shower, this space exudes tranquility and relaxation. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests, with plenty of natural light and closet space. A second bathroom, also completely renovated, adds to the overall convenience and comfort of this home.But the beauty doesn't end indoors! Step outside onto the spacious patio, where you'll find the perfect spot for al fresco dining or simply enjoying the beautiful Florida weather. The expansive patio and delightful garden area with a luxurious screen in pool makes it a true oasis for those seeking outdoor living. Conveniently situated near top-rated schools, shopping centers, dining options, and recreational facilities. With easy access to major highways, commuting to nearby cities or attractions is a breeze. We can't wait to welcome you to the neighborhood!
